{"tid":1458011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望比狗射爆眼既女仔家人可以出黎開個記者會","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T15:01:54.000Z","uid":19527,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"dd3b0fad1ce15e8ddb399b4c6f64eaab0dfef5b9","tid":1458011,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:46:02.000Z","msg":"而家好多淺藍都信哂個女仔係比自己人射傷<br />\n黑警仲好串咀咁話證實唔到係比子彈射傷<br />\n連中央電影台都用埋呢單假新聞<br />\n我明白你地可能因為唔想太高調或者各種原因唔想咁做<br />\n但係呢一單野我地真係好嬲，好嬲點解呢個政權可以指鹿為馬到咁既地步<br />\n希望你地可以為左香港，行出黎幫香港人攞返個真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258f8f60c45319439ebc90453674f856a228a5f1","tid":1458011,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5388b0b9cf95d79392588dd0cc04834ce71fb8a3","tid":1458011,"uid":10805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:54:11.000Z","msg":"要瘋狂抽插警犬"},{"pid":"c2a9fbe03d34b27ece2395320413dee2df00bae6","tid":1458011,"uid":389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:54:48.000Z","msg":"佢地未必想比人起全家"},{"pid":"2fc405f12986c13381954ecf8d4410f6949fce4d","tid":1458011,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:55:02.000Z","msg":"呢個真係好重要，推"},{"pid":"9a126ea2f888cafdb755d7fd0743e2c1cc15bc28","tid":1458011,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c2a9fbe03d34b27ece2395320413dee2df00bae6","tid":1458011,"uid":389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:54:48.000Z","msg":"佢地未必想比人起全家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:55:37.000Z","msg":"我都明會有呢種憂慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c1b359ab8e6405d7c2ac6a08ff34b3af921be8","tid":1458011,"uid":46385,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:5